<img class="hide" src="/files/images/clear.gif" width="1" height="1" alt="" /><h2><img width="190" alt="Case histories" height="80" border="0" src="/files/images/XM_L3_Clients_histories_shdr.gif" /></h2><p><strong>Chanel</strong></p><p>We were asked by Chanel to create an online banner campaign to create awareness of their brand 'Chance'.</p><p>This project was dependant on carefully managing the brand and allying this with an understanding of the target audience and the environment.</p><p>We achieved this through rich media banners which were placed prominently on related sites such as glamour.com and getlippy.com.</p><p>The campaign was focused around 'Take a Chance' in which we created an online invitation which visitors could register to enter a competition to win a Chanel make over and other goodies.</p><p><img alt="Chanel Chance Banner Ad" border="0" height="308" src="/files/images/Chanel 1.jpg" width="250" /> </p><p> </p><p><img alt="Chanel Chance Landing Page" border="0" height="162" src="/files/images/Chanel 2.jpg" width="256" /></p><img class="hide" src="/files/images/clear.gif" width="1" height="1" alt="" />
